## 시스템프로그래밍 file discripter 이해하기

### It is a assignment for understanding file discriptors    I used the hotel frontdesk as an example   The purpose is to allow the guest file to be changed according to the situation.

#### situation 
* Check the current situation in the room.
* There is no room that the guest wants.
* There is room that the guest wants, so change the file.
* Make the room that corresopnds to the guest name vacant.
* If the guest name don't match, print it out 
